62
00:04:40,240 --> 00:04:40,830
By the way,

63
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:42,680
why did you

64
00:04:43,070 --> 00:04:44,160
press the alarm yesterday?

65
00:04:44,870 --> 00:04:46,870
