66
00:04:46,870 --> 00:04:48,360
so I can't directly ask him

67
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:49,950
if he's the one who saved me.

68
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:54,630
It's because you came back so late,

69
00:04:54,630 --> 00:04:56,070
and I was worried about you...

70
00:04:58,560 --> 00:04:59,310
What about you?

71
00:04:59,430 --> 00:05:01,240
