73
00:05:04,630 --> 00:05:06,160
But I didn't see who it was.

74
00:05:08,430 --> 00:05:10,070
Let me take care of your hand.

75
00:05:25,190 --> 00:05:27,240
It couldn't have been

76
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,830
my stepmom.

77
00:05:29,510 --> 00:05:31,680
Was it Cui Zihao?

78
00:05:51,950 --> 00:05:54,160
I've gotten familiar with the people
in the village.

79
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:56,560
It's time to start the acquisition plan.

80
00:05:59,630 --> 00:06:01,560
Those people are getting closer
to the village.

81
00:06:01,870 --> 00:06:04,040
I need to find out who's behind this.

82
00:06:12,190 --> 00:06:13,360
Do you have plans for today?

83
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:15,480
I'm going to town

84
00:06:16,510 --> 00:06:18,040
to check on the tea market.

85
00:06:18,430 --> 00:06:19,480
I'll cook dinner tonight for you.

86
00:06:19,870 --> 00:06:20,680
What about you?

87
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:22,430
Then...

88
00:06:22,630 --> 00:06:23,870
I'll go to the tea plantation.

89
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:26,040
If any customers come,

90
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:27,240
I can watch over them for you.

91
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:28,360
See you tonight then.

92
00:06:32,300 --> 00:06:35,660
[Guyan Tea Plantation]

93
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:38,160
Come on, aunties, you must be exhausted.

94
00:06:38,950 --> 00:06:40,190
Come sit down and have some food.

95
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:43,070
Have something to eat, come on.

96
00:06:43,310 --> 00:06:44,120
Thank you.

97
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:45,360
Help yourself, take some.

98
00:06:45,630 --> 00:06:46,560
Take some, take.

99
00:06:47,000 --> 00:06:47,190
Come on.

100
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:51,070
Sit down.

101
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:53,720
You must be exhausted. It's very hot.

102
00:06:54,160 --> 00:06:55,310
The sun is so strong today.

103
00:06:55,310 --> 00:06:56,830
Yes, it's very hot today.

104
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:58,240
Xiufen,

105
00:06:58,750 --> 00:07:00,750
you've been back for so long,
but we haven't had a good chat.

106
00:07:00,800 --> 00:07:02,750
We've been busy picking tea every day.

107
00:07:02,750 --> 00:07:04,950
That's true. You know,
since she came back,

108
00:07:04,950 --> 00:07:05,600
she's been busy.

109
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:06,870
Yes, I've been busy since I got back.

110
00:07:06,870 --> 00:07:08,190
So I'll be honest.

111
00:07:08,190 --> 00:07:09,950
I came back for a reason this time.

112
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,120
I wanted

113
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:14,870
to divide the family property with them.

114
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:18,040
But I don't know

115
00:07:18,040 --> 00:07:19,680
about the house and land prices,

116
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:21,360
or anything about planting tea
and trees.

117
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:22,360
I don't understand.

118
00:07:22,750 --> 00:07:23,510
That's true.

119
00:07:23,510 --> 00:07:25,000
She hasn't been back for so many years,

120
00:07:25,000 --> 00:07:25,830
how could she know?

121
00:07:25,830 --> 00:07:26,360
Of course she wouldn't know.

122
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:27,360
She hasn't been back for so long.

123
00:07:27,630 --> 00:07:28,870
We can help you.

124
00:07:29,070 --> 00:07:29,870
Really?

125
00:07:30,830 --> 00:07:32,270
Our tea plantation

126
00:07:32,270 --> 00:07:34,310
produces about 300 to 500 jin

127
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:36,800
per mu each year.

128
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:40,680
And the contracting price
for the tea plantation

129
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:43,160
is about 1,000 to 1,500 yuan per mu.

130
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:44,360
Right.

131
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:46,720
Now you can roughly calculate it, right?

132
00:07:46,870 --> 00:07:48,510
So you should have an idea

133
00:07:48,510 --> 00:07:50,560
how much your fields are worth, right?

134
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:51,600
Yes.

135
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:52,560
Right.

136
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:02,270
Buddy.

137
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:04,480
Let's go.

138
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:08,270
We work for them every day

139
00:08:08,430 --> 00:08:09,720
and get knocked out from time to time.

140
00:08:10,270 --> 00:08:11,870
When will it end?

141
00:08:14,430 --> 00:08:16,360
How about we also lease a piece of land

142
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:17,310
and not go back?

143
00:08:17,510 --> 00:08:18,270
Lease a piece of land?

144
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:20,160
Alright.

145
00:08:20,270 --> 00:08:21,870
Let's go.

146
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:33,360
Time to go home and cook.

147
00:08:37,580 --> 00:08:39,700
[Real-time video]

148
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:42,870
We meet again.

149
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:47,320
Moonflowers for you.

150
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:48,870
Moonflower?

151
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:51,750
Are you mistaking me for Ye Xiyan again?

152
00:08:54,630 --> 00:08:55,790
You two look very similar.

153
00:08:56,270 --> 00:08:57,910
That's a kind of fate in itself.

154
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:00,360
There are many kinds of fate.

155
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:02,120
Forcing it is not beautiful.

156
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:03,440
Also,

157
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:05,360
stop having your people follow me

158
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:06,960
and pretend to run into me.

159
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:14,670
Your delicate hands

160
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:16,870
don't have any calluses.

161
00:09:17,750 --> 00:09:19,270
You don't look like you've worked
in the fields.

162
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:24,870
I had a job and rarely worked
in the fields,

163
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,750
so my hands healed. Is there a problem?

164
00:09:27,790 --> 00:09:29,600
Even if you can't find Ye Xiyan,

165
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:30,960
there's no need to prove

166
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:32,240
I'm her, right?

167
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:34,200
Fine.

168
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,870
Then let's just be new friends

169
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:39,720
and get to know each other.

170
00:09:40,030 --> 00:09:41,270
We can chat, right?

171
00:09:42,030 --> 00:09:42,840
I...

172
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:44,720
That depends on
whether my fiancée agrees.

173
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:46,120
Stop bothering her,

174
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:47,550
or I'll take measures.

175
00:09:55,750 --> 00:09:57,000
I'm just walking here.

176
00:09:57,870 --> 00:09:58,790
Is there a problem?

177
00:10:00,550 --> 00:10:01,320
Also,

178
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:03,750
if I want,

179
00:10:04,510 --> 00:10:06,150
I can buy this place.

180
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:17,360
Name your price.

181
00:10:18,080 --> 00:10:19,360
I want this beach.

182
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:21,480
I'll have to ask my boss.

183
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:22,200
Alright.

184
00:10:23,870 --> 00:10:24,790
Sir, what do you think?

185
00:10:29,550 --> 00:10:30,320
No.

186
00:10:31,030 --> 00:10:32,360
You're not welcome here.

187
00:10:36,630 --> 00:10:37,440
Fine.

188
00:10:38,360 --> 00:10:39,550
You're hiding your true strength.

189
00:10:39,600 --> 00:10:41,360
It seems we need
to get to know each other again.

190
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:43,480
My name is Lu Mingyu,

191
00:10:43,630 --> 00:10:44,870
Xiufen's fiancé.

192
00:10:46,670 --> 00:10:47,720
Remember that.

193
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:32,750
Mingyu, how are things going
with Xiufen?

194
00:11:33,670 --> 00:11:34,360
Not bad.

195
00:11:34,360 --> 00:11:35,080
Xiufen,

196
00:11:35,870 --> 00:11:37,360
you're really into him, huh?

197
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:42,320
What? I'm just enjoying the view.

198
00:11:43,510 --> 00:11:44,910
Didn't you say you had something
to talk to me about?

199
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:46,030
Yes.

200
00:11:47,270 --> 00:11:48,510
My short video account

201
00:11:48,510 --> 00:11:49,870
hasn't been getting much traffic.

202
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:52,200
I really don't know what to do.

203
00:11:58,360 --> 00:11:59,440
Your problem is

204
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:00,000
you're always

205
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:02,150
copying other people's styles.

206
00:12:02,870 --> 00:12:03,870
You should have

207
00:12:03,870 --> 00:12:05,600
your own unique style as Su Qiqi.

208
00:12:06,870 --> 00:12:07,720
That's right.

209
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:10,080
Then give me some advice.

210
00:12:10,750 --> 00:12:13,150
I want to ask a question.

211
00:12:14,870 --> 00:12:15,910
I have a friend

212
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:20,960
who has a crush on the girl
he grew up with.

213
00:12:21,510 --> 00:12:24,200
What do you think his chances are?

214
00:12:24,200 --> 00:12:25,550
Do you like Su Qiqi?

215
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:28,960
Is it that obvious?

216
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:33,600
Your rate of success

217
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:35,510
is proportional to your effort.

218
00:12:35,960 --> 00:12:36,790
You have to work hard.

219
00:12:38,200 --> 00:12:40,080
For example, you could do

220
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:42,790
a series on traditional culture
in modern life.

221
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:46,630
There's a traditional painting
in Mingyu's study.

222
00:12:46,630 --> 00:12:47,600
I'll bring it over for you.

223
00:12:47,750 --> 00:12:48,550
Alright.

224
00:12:59,200 --> 00:13:00,030
Xiufen!

225
00:13:12,750 --> 00:13:13,550
Are you OK?

226
00:13:15,790 --> 00:13:17,030
I'm fine.

227
00:13:17,030 --> 00:13:21,320
But where did these flowers come from?

228
00:13:21,360 --> 00:13:22,150
I bought them.

229
00:13:22,600 --> 00:13:23,480
Do you like them?

230
00:13:26,550 --> 00:13:29,510
Create a crisis if there's none.

231
00:13:30,030 --> 00:13:30,910
I've learned that.

232
00:13:36,550 --> 00:13:38,000
Qiqi, watch out.

233
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:45,870
It seems not everyone can do this.

234
00:13:45,870 --> 00:13:46,720
Jiang Shengsheng!

235
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:48,270
Su Qiqi,

236
00:13:48,790 --> 00:13:49,870
I didn't do it on purpose.

237
00:13:49,870 --> 00:13:50,960
I saw you spill it.

238
00:13:50,960 --> 00:13:52,030
And you say it wasn't on purpose!

239
00:13:52,030 --> 00:13:53,200
You, stop there!

240
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:54,480
I really didn't do it on purpose.

241
00:13:54,550 --> 00:13:55,510
Stop running!

242
00:13:55,900 --> 00:13:59,460
♪We're just so right for each other♪

243
00:14:00,100 --> 00:14:04,220
♪Will kissing you feel like
tasting a fruit?♪

244
00:14:04,220 --> 00:14:05,340
[Chapter 10: Tender Proposal]

245
00:14:05,340 --> 00:14:09,420
♪My little bear, you're so precious♪

246
00:14:10,060 --> 00:14:12,940
♪But little bear, little bear♪

247
00:14:13,260 --> 00:14:17,260
♪They always have so many rules
about love♪

248
00:14:17,270 --> 00:14:18,080
Xiufen,

249
00:14:18,240 --> 00:14:19,510
I made you some snacks.

250
00:14:21,030 --> 00:14:21,870
What's this?

251
00:14:24,790 --> 00:14:25,600
Lu Mingyu.

252
00:14:38,060 --> 00:14:40,820
♪When I opened my eyes,
I saw your heart suddenly crowded♪

253
00:14:41,420 --> 00:14:44,340
♪Each stroke of what word
gradually becomes clear♪

254
00:14:44,780 --> 00:14:47,860
♪After 300 thousand time units,
wishes ignite shooting stars♪

255
00:14:48,300 --> 00:14:51,460
♪When cherry blossom petals fall,
they travel much more than 5cm♪

256
00:14:51,900 --> 00:14:54,740
♪Planets attract each other,
bringing us closer together♪

257
00:14:55,100 --> 00:14:58,340
♪Love is like a lighter,
a touch creates an echo♪

258
00:14:58,860 --> 00:15:01,380
♪I've also walked alone
through lost dreams♪

259
00:15:01,820 --> 00:15:04,180
♪Finally awakening because of you♪

260
00:15:04,620 --> 00:15:08,180
♪As swift as a monsoon,
you suddenly appear♪

261
00:15:08,460 --> 00:15:11,700
♪Raindrops from across the sea
give me all the courage♪

262
00:15:11,980 --> 00:15:14,900
♪Kissing your eyes
as our shoulders meet♪

263
00:15:15,180 --> 00:15:18,340
♪My traces are in your starry sky♪

264
00:15:18,540 --> 00:15:22,020
♪Like the night sky summoning
shooting stars, you descend for me♪

265
00:15:22,380 --> 00:15:25,460
♪Standing at the world's center,
I hold your hand in mine♪

266
00:15:25,820 --> 00:15:29,060
♪The sound of heartbeats hitting walls♪

267
00:15:29,420 --> 00:15:34,820
♪That feeling is probably called love♪
